org.bonitasoft.engine.bpm.flownode

Interface FlowElementContainerDefinition

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BaseElement, BonitaObject, Serializable, Visitable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    FlowElementContainerDefinition
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    FlowElementContainerDefinitionImpl

    public interface FlowElementContainerDefinition
extends BaseElement, Visitable
    Allows to access all flow elements (activities, gateways, events and transitions) of a process or sub-process.
    Author:
    Matthieu Chaffotte, Celine Souchet
